## Translation Rules

### Structure Preservation

- Maintain ALL heading levels exactly (H1, H2, H3, etc.)
- Preserve code blocks (fenced with triple backticks) — do NOT translate their contents
- Keep list formatting (ordered and unordered) intact
- Preserve horizontal rules (`---`)
