### Technical Terms — Keep in English

The following terms MUST remain in English (do not translate):

- Git, branch, merge, pull request, commit, tag, rebase
- Tool names: Rust, Bevy, RON, TOML, ECS, egui, cargo test
- Code identifiers: variable names, function names, command-line arguments, struct/enum names
